Titolo: Combat School

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Combat School, released as Boot Camp in North America, is a 1987 arcade game produced by Konami where the player takes control of a military recruit who is undergoing basic training at a United States Marine Corps Recruit Training camp, also known as a boot camp. The arcade game uses trackball controls.
In 1987, Ocean Software released ports of the game for the Commodore 64, ZX Spectrum and Amstrad CPC in Europe. Konami themselves later released the Commodore 64 version in North America under the Boot Camp title in 1989 alongside an MS-DOS version. An Amiga version was announced, but never released.